achievementsGuide.description: Achievements are sorted into four tiers based on XP. Platinum is awarded by Epic upon earning 1000 XP in a game.

achievements.title: After the Fall
achievements.description: Fall from a combined height of at least 10,994 meters.

achievements.title: Bing Bang Boom!
achievements.description: Perform an Air Kick after a Double Wall Run.

achievements.title: Boot Licker
achievements.description: Reach City Alignment 7 for any faction.

achievements.title: Can't Touch This!
achievements.description: Kill 20 enemies in a row with melee weapons without taking damage.

achievements.title: Can't You Read the Signs?
achievements.description: Collect all Inhibitors hidden in GRE Quarantines.

achievements.title: Death From Afar
achievements.description: Kill a Spitter using a ranged weapon.

achievements.title: Don't Look Up
achievements.description: Perform Smash on at least 50 enemies.

achievements.title: First Shot
achievements.description: Use an Inhibitor for the first time.

achievements.title: It Wasn't That Hard, Was It?
Lightning Reflexes
achievements.description: Perform a Perfect Block 10 times in a row without taking damage.

achievements.title: Man On a Mission
achievements.description: Meet all your Sparker love interests.

achievements.title: Modder
achievements.description: Modify your weapons at least 50 times.

achievements.title: Oh, So This Is How It Works!
achievements.description: Modify your weapon for the first time.

achievements.title: Slowpoke!
achievements.description: Lose the maximum level of Chase.

achievements.title: Tanning Salon
achievements.description: Use the UV Flashlight to kill a Viral.

achievements.title: Terminal Headache
achievements.description: Perform 50 headshots with a ranged weapon.

achievements.title: That's Teamwork!
achievements.description: Kill 100 enemies while playing with at least 2 other players.

achievements.title: Tickets, Please!
achievements.description: Use a Metro Station to Fast Travel.

achievements.title: Your World, Your Rules
achievements.description: Complete the game with any ending.
